            <title>[SOLR-14253] Remove Sleeps from OverseerCollectionMessageHandler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-14253</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From the conversations with Mark Miller a few months back - there are a lot of places in the server code where we have hard sleeps instead of relying on notifications and watchers to handle state.&lt;/p&gt;

